<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>界面快报</title><link>https://jiemian.com/</link><description>界面快报</description><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><image><url>https://res.jiemian.com/assets/wap/common/img/jm-new-logo.png</url><title>界面快报</title><link>https://jiemian.com/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 00:30:03 +0800</lastBuildDate><pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 00:30:03 +0800</pubDate><item><title>星狮物流商产信托展望评级被下调至负面</title><link>https://www.jiemian.com/article/11989049.html</link><description><![CDATA[<div class="article-content"><p>11月14日，星狮物流商产信托（FLCT）在新交所公告，信托展望评级被下调至负面。信托管理层指出，标普（S&amp;P）确认了信托的发行人信用评级及其担保的高级无抵押票据为“BBB+”评级，同时将信托的评级展望从“稳定”下调为“负面”。（联合早报）</p>
